Streak Calculation (Internal Logic):
  habit_id      : 1
  habit_name    : Morning Run
  Checking logs from latest date backwards...
 
  2025-04-24 -> DONE    (streak continues)
  2025-04-23 -> DONE    (streak continues)
  2025-04-22 -> DONE    (streak continues)
  2025-04-21 -> DONE    (streak continues)
  2025-04-20 -> DONE    (streak continues)
  2025-04-19 -> MISSED  (streak broken — stop)
 
  Current Streak : 5 days
  Longest Streak : 7 days
 
Response:
  {
    "status": "success",
    "habit_id": 1,
    "habit_name": "Morning Run",
    "current_streak": 5,
    "longest_streak": 7,
    "last_completed": "2025-04-24"
  }
 
SQLite Query Executed:
  SELECT date, status FROM habit_logs
  WHERE habit_id = 1
  ORDER BY date DESC;
 
 
